description:
My HoneyDew this week is Adam Ferrara! Adam returns to highlight the lowlights about his anxiety and depression. We talk about his panic attacks, therapy and the medication no one seems to have for our specific symptoms.

I hope y’all have a very Merry Christmas! Every sangle one of ya’s deserves it! It’s been an absurd year! To hell with 2020’s funky ass!
